    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a full turn action, you can superheat your blood to cauterize your injuries.</p><p> You gain 4 flurry die of temporary hit points and you can suspend the effects of any two conditions you are under the effects of, excluding Grappled, Restrained, and Exhaustion, negating the condition's effects until you lose a number of hit points equal to 10 + your character level, after which this style ends.</p><p> You can only benefit from this style once at a time.</p><p></p>",
